4.2 ATTENDANCE AND LEAVE MANAGEMENT
================================================================================
ID     | User Story / Requirement                              | Status      | Evidence in hrmodule
-------|-------------------------------------------------------|-------------|------------------------------------------
4.2.1  | Attendance tracking — manual / mobile check-in        | IMPLEMENTED | Remote clock-in/out (submitRemoteClockIn), biometric log processing, team calendar grid. UI: Attendance.jsx tabs (calendar, remote, biometric, networks).
4.2.2  | Leave types: Casual, Sick, Paid, Unpaid               | PARTIAL     | Leave types seeded as Casual Leave (CL), Medical Leave (ML), Earned Leave (EL). Admin can configure plans/definitions. PDF-specific Sick/Paid/Unpaid naming not matched exactly.
4.2.3  | Approval workflows: Employee → Manager → HR           | PARTIAL     | Attendance regularization has approve/reject (processRegularization). NO employee leave application request + multi-level approval chain.
4.2.4  | Reports: Attendance summary / Leave balance           | PARTIAL     | Team calendar matrix + attendance events exist. Leave balance report per employee NOT implemented. No dedicated attendance summary export.

EXTRA (not in PDF):
  - Biometric hardware device registry (create/delete devices)
  - IP network whitelist for remote check-in validation
  - Attendance settings (biometric mode, IP validation toggle)
  - Attendance regularization appeals (request + approve/reject)

