4.3 PAYROLL MANAGEMENT
================================================================================
ID     | User Story / Requirement                              | Status      | Evidence in hrmodule
-------|-------------------------------------------------------|-------------|------------------------------------------
4.3.1  | Salary structure: Fixed + variable (incentives)       | PARTIAL     | basicSalary + allowances + deductions model exists. Allowances are generic — no separate "incentive" component tied to performance.
4.3.2  | Incentive calculation based on enrolments / revenue   | MISSING     | calculatePayroll() uses static salary structures only. No enrolment count or revenue data pulled from Student/Marketing modules.
