4.3.4  | Payslip generation                                    | IMPLEMENTED | POST /payroll/execute (calculatePayroll), GET /payroll/payslips, PayrollInputs.jsx with statement viewer + print.

EXTRA (not in PDF):
  - Monthly batch execution UI with payout statistics dashboard
  - Payslip detail modal with credit/debit component breakdown

